            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "That `run_simple` is called is an implementation detail and irrelevant to the user of the method. Apart from that the tests, test almost nothing even based on the things they could test with mocking `run_simple`.\n\nA useful test would not use any mocking at all and actually test that it does as the documentation claims, that is run the application in a server, which communicates via HTTP on the host and port given, that the reloader works depending on arguments and configuration etc.\n"
        },
